Rating: 3
Quick, easy & a crowd pleaser. This is a great recipe and beats out another one called Cherry-Vanilla Bean Ice Cream with Cherry Sauce (which takes hours and hours to make...for pretty much the same taste as Vanilla ice cream with warm cherry sauce. I've tried both and find the results are about the same except this recipe is a fraction of the time as the other. Definite keeper.

